{"questions": [{"q_type": "label", "q_order": 1, "q_title": "Add your comments here", "q_values": [{"q_type": "textarea", "q_title": "", "required": false, "q_ans_value": " Serious Adverse events (SAEs) must be reported from the time the patient provides informed consent through and including\n28 calendar days after the last administration of the study drug.
